    "description": "<strong>Gastro Run</strong> is a fast-paced educational adventure game full of obstacles, boss fights, races, with<br>lessons placed throughout the game. You play as Gastro, a witty nano-bot whose goal is to help <br>patients with enzyme deficiency break down food as it travels through the digestive system. <br>Enter the human’s GI tract and shoot enzymes as you observe how food breaks down in different <br>organs. <br>Race Nutrient stealing “leechers” in the winding twists and turns of the small intestine. <br>Defend the stomach walls from attacking germs to finally cure the patient.<br>This game will test your flying and shooting accuracy while teaching you about the human digestive <br>system.<br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br>● Shoot enzymes to break down food and defeat germs <br>● Collect booster bubbles and fly past nutrient stealing leechers!<br>● Collect stars at the end of each level and unlock rewards and upgrades!<br>● Avoid obstacles like incoming food and fly through intestinal blockages!<br>● Watch out for clues and hints during popup videos!<br>● A Unique combination of fun &amp; learning.",
